Note (Т5, audit): this project had no license at all before this file was
added, leaving its legal status for reuse/contribution genuinely undefined.
MIT was picked as a permissive, low-friction default matching how this
project is already shared (a personal/hobby tool, no existing statement of
intent otherwise) - swap this file for a different license if that's not
actually what you want; nothing else in the repo assumes MIT specifically.
